text: Skip the morning muffin, and take on the day like a Rachel Homan with this protein-packed smoothie.
Rich, creamy taste, long-lasting energy. That’s what Team Homan calls a win, win.
Coconut, apricots and oats are combined to form satisfying bite-size clusters that will give you a BOOST any time of the day.
Add protein powder to chocolate chip cookies to make them feel like a healthier indulgence.
Chia seeds for protein and fiber, fresh pineapple and mango for game-winning taste.
